---
title: Golden Coconut Beef & Veggie Udon Noodles with Crushed Peanuts & Coriander
description: Everything is glittering and golden tonight, with ropes of udon noodles coiled in a coconutty broth with tender beef. It’s brimming with delicious pops of veggies like baby broccoli and carrot. Sprinle over some crushed peanuts to make this dish shine at your table.
